5d7f730d647405c62955edef99ffa9ce44b14035.query:
INSERT INTO executed_l1_events
        (
            l1_block_number,
            l1_batch_number,
            l2_range_begin,
            l2_range_end
        )
        VALUES ( $1, $2, $3, $4 )

5e5de8445de431a5679b48fb85160f3bdb42fef3.query:
INSERT INTO withdrawals
        (
            tx_hash,
            block_number,
            token,
            amount,
            event_index_in_tx,
            committed_in_block,
            verified_in_block,
            executed_in_block
        )
        VALUES (
            $1, $2, $3, $4, $5,
            (
                SELECT l1_block_number
                FROM committed_l1_events
                WHERE l2_range_begin <= $2 AND l2_range_end >= $2
            ),
            (
                SELECT l1_block_number
                FROM verified_l1_events
                WHERE l2_range_begin <= $2 AND l2_range_end >= $2
            ),
            (
                SELECT l1_block_number
                FROM executed_l1_events
                WHERE l2_range_begin <= $2 AND l2_range_end >= $2
            )
        )
        ON CONFLICT (tx_hash, block_number, event_index_in_tx) DO NOTHING

UPDATE withdrawals
        SET verified_in_block=$1
        WHERE block_number >= $2 AND block_number <= $3
